My wife has been craving for fried liver for about two weeks ago. We were heading out for breakfast. As we were driving thru Sistrunk, I remembered this place that had the best chicken gizzards and liver. My wife stated that there was a place called BG’s that sold fried liver. We actually passed the restaurant talking about it. We turned around and pulled into the parking lot. They were open! We ordered the chicken gizzards/ liver platter with fries and two large lemonades. The hospitality was great and the food was so amazing. My wife, son and I ate the food as soon as we got in the truck. We were full and forgot breakfast. I would definitely recommend this place for great food. My family and I love supporting our black businesses in our black communities. Go out and try it!!!!
